    {
      "id": "sybil_1_listing_1",
      "firm_id": "sybil_1",
      "description": "Hey there! I'm parting ways with my trusty ride, and she's been such a joy to drive. It's in really solid shape and has been super reliable for me. If you're looking for a dependable car that still looks great on the road, this is the one! Feel free to ask any questions\u2014I'd love to see it go to a good home.",
      "price": 32000.0,
