      "description": "Hey there! I'm looking to find a new home for my trusty car. It\u2019s been such a reliable ride for me and is still in really solid shape, both inside and out. It drives smoothly and has been well-cared for over the years. If you're looking for a dependable set of wheels that still looks great on the road, this is the one for you! Feel free to reach out with any questions or if you want to come by and take it for a spin!",
      "price": 33500.0,
