    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_7_listing_7",
      "firm_id": "sybil_7",
      "description": "Up for sale is a mechanically robust 2008 Chevrolet Corvette Z06, a platform defined by its LS7 7.0L V8 and its high-revving 7,000 RPM redline. This unit features the factory dry-sump lubrication system and titanium connecting rods, ensuring oil pressure stability under high lateral G-loads. The aluminum-intensive chassis remains rigid, paired with a Tremec TR-6060 6-speed manual transmission that shifts crisply. While the exterior shows minor road wear consistent with a 'good' condition driver, the powertrain is dialed in with recently verified valve guide clearances and a set of fresh Michelin Pilot Sport 4S tires. It retains the factory-spec 505 hp and 470 lb-ft of torque, offering an unfiltered analog driving experience for the serious enthusiast.",
